title: Grateful Dead Live at Community War Memorial Auditorium on 1981-09-26
lineage: Maxell XLIIS > Nakamichi CR-5A > Edirol FA-66 >  Wavelab > R8Brain > CD-Wave > TLH > FLAC 1644 Tagged.
description:
Set 1

Shakedown Street-> CC Rider, They Love Each Other, Cassidy, Jack A Roe, On The Road Again, Ramble On Rose, Looks Like Rain, Brown Eyed Women, Let It Grow-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Playin' In The Band-> Bertha-> Estimated Prophet-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Drums-> Not Fade Away-> Morning Dew-> Playin' In The Band-> One More Saturday Night, E: Johnny B. Goode

reviews.review_text: Upstaged the stones The dead added this show in the middle of the tour. The kinks played Thursday  the dead played Saturday and the stones played Sunday . I seen all three and the dead killed them all!!! Look at the fucking set list
